rows.label: tlk43700241_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Y-you really taught me a lesson
back there.

rows.label: tlk43700241_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I lost because I wasn't able to fully
make use of my Assist Cores.

rows.label: tlk43700241_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I could have equipped something with
a fire-damage reduction effect to
weaken the Holy Grail's attacks...

rows.label: tlk43700241_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Or I could have used a jamming effect
to dodge ranged attacks. If I'd done
something like that, I would have won!

rows.label: tlk43700241_01_msg0006
rows.name:
That's not to say I'm going to try it,
but believe me, it's true!
